        "infoContent": "<div style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 60ch;text-align: left;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://seagl.org/\"><img alt=\"SeaGL 2020\" src=\"static/themes/seagl/logo.svg\" width=\"200\" height=\"184\" style=\"height: 7em; width: auto;\" /></a></p><p>SeaGL’s chat is available via both <a href=\"https://matrix.org/\">Matrix</a> and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Relay_Chat\">IRC</a>. The rooms are <a href=\"https://matrix.org/bridges/\"><i>bridged</i></a> so you can use either protocol.</p><div style=\"display: grid;grid-gap: 1em;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\"><div><h3>Matrix</h3><p>Join <a href=\"https://matrix.to/#/#SeaGL:seattlematrix.org\"><code>#SeaGL:seattlematrix.org</code></a> in your preferred client.</p></div><div><h3>IRC</h3><p>Join <a href=\"ircs://irc.libera.chat:6697/#SeaGL\"><code>#SeaGL</code></a> on <a href=\"https://libera.chat/\">Libera.Chat</a> in your preferred client, or continue <span class=\"hide-small\">to the right</span><span class=\"show-small\">below</span>.</p></div></div>",
        "greetingText": "Join via IRC",
        "footerText": "<p>Our chat takes place on the <a href=\"https://libera.chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Libera.Chat</a> IRC network, a public space shared by thousands of other people. Please be mindful of SeaGL’s <a href=\"https://seagl.org/code_of_conduct\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">code of conduct</a> and Libera.Chat’s own <a href=\"https://libera.chat/policies\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">policies</a>, as we are guests in this space.</p><h3 class=\"muted\">Choosing an IRC <i>nick</i></h3><p class=\"muted\">An IRC <i>nick</i> (or <i>nickname</i>) is a publicly visible username. If your chosen name is already in use or has been <a href=\"https://libera.chat/guides/registration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reserved</a> by someone else, you'll be notified after connecting. You can change it at any time; it’s normal for there to be some shuffling around.</p><p class=\"muted\">Requirements: Up to 16 characters from among <code>A</code>–<code>Z</code>, <code>a</code>–<code>z</code>, <code>0</code>–<code>9</code>, <code>-</code>, or <code>_</code>, beginning with a letter</p>"
    },

